item.description:
All the C++ code were done using the C++14 version. To compile use the following command:
g++ -std=c++14 &lt;INPUT_FILE_NAME&gt; -o &lt;OUTPUT_FILE_NAME&gt; And to run the code:
./&lt;OUTPUT_FILE_NAME&gt;

To compile use the following command:
kotlinc &lt;INPUT_FILE_NAME&gt; -include-runtime -d &lt;OUTPUT_FILE_NAME&gt;.jar And to run the code:
java -jar &lt;OUTPUT_FILE_NAME&gt;
